{"tid":1753184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"范國威呼籲議員聲援理大","createTime":"2019-11-25T01:45:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T05:46:24.000Z","uid":184679,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"749e7595f3760b9064acc6bb7aad0388f898b7a7","tid":1753184,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:45:19.000Z","msg":"西貢區選舉結果陸續出爐，新民主同盟范國威在運亨選區勝出。他呼籲新當選的區議員，明日下午4點去理大附近百週年紀念花園集會，要求政府正視區選結果民意海嘯，回應五大訴求，並促請警察退場，救救受困年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n另外，新民主同盟在當區已有多人當選，包括健明選區的梁里、欣英選區的鍾錦麟、康景選區的林少忠、澳唐選區的呂文光、軍澳選區的黎銘澤、慧茵選區的秦海城、海晉選區的黎煒棠及寶林選區的馮君安。<br />\n<br />\n另外，工黨何偉航亦在白沙灣勝出。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1645282/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%A5%BF%E8%B2%A2%E5%8D%80%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C-%E6%96%B0%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E5%90%8C%E7%9B%9F%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E7%8D%B2%E5%8B%9D-%E8%8C%83%E5%9C%8B%E5%A8%81%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E8%81%B2%E6%8F%B4%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7</code></pre>"},{"pid":"3c151fe7d8ddffa780a90c92d4e299d63af8fb94","tid":1753184,"uid":46042,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:46:59.000Z","msg":"300個議員全部即刻去<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係選你哋嚟做乜"},{"pid":"277bd18092b6d73d197890ae5bbb15dc0a3fbe63","tid":1753184,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:48:49.000Z","msg":"保皇輸到咁<br />\n係時候植入拒絕西方民主思想<br />\n<br />\n點建得泛民有熱狗？"},{"pid":"7fe761e21c939aca0f7a02b28141f392e552cc21","tid":1753184,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:50:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a6c01eee9ab4e52ffef2958cdb69fb1b54bcce","tid":1753184,"uid":51111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:51:52.000Z","msg":"(行動post) 今晚poly定十八區商場？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1753155\" data-